data.description: Beautiful home to call yours! Local builder Discover Homes presents ''The Gibson'' plan. This 4 bedroom, 3 bath home, with a bonus room, has everything today's homeowner's are looking for. The floorplan is open and functional. Kitchen has shaker cabinets, soft close drawers, stainless steel appliances, large working island, granite countertops and a farmhouse sink. Split bedroom layout downstairs with a bonus room and full bath upstairs.  Estimated to be completed end of November. Gretchen Pines is a new gated community in Moore County close to Pinehurst and Seven Lakes.
